Troubleshooting
Common Issues:

CUDA errors: Use CPU-only requirements if GPU unavailable
Memory issues: Reduce batch size in training parameters
Poor quality results: Increase training iterations or use higher resolution source material
Alignment failures: Ensure faces are clearly visible and well-lit in source videos
